# Environment shared by the production web service (panel) and the reconcile sweep,
# referenced by both through EnvironmentFile= so the tenant they impersonate and the
# roster they read cannot drift between them. Rendered per stage from the encrypted
# secrets; systemd reads it as root at unit start, so the file itself stays root-only.
SOLIDARITY_TECH_REQUEST_BUDGET=50
# The real portlanddsa.org tenant admin the DWD service account impersonates.
ROSADMIN_GOOGLE_SUBJECT=${google_dwd_subject}
